174
00:14:50,930 --> 00:14:52,300
so now they wait to see you.

175
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:54,390
No. No. I'm not--

176
00:14:55,220 --> 00:14:57,680
Lin, no-- no problem waiting, Linbaba. -I can't.

177
00:14:57,770 --> 00:15:00,690
