184
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:19,250
Even bad doctor better than no doctor.

185
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:23,040
I'm not saying you are bad, only that if you were, it would be okay.

186
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:25,460
Lin, please.

187
00:15:27,010 --> 00:15:29,680
Prabhu. -Lakshmi was going to die anyway.

188
00:15:30,380 --> 00:15:32,010
And we will grieve her.

189
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:35,220
But that is how it is sometimes.

190
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:41,980
How are you, Prabhu? -Okay.

191
00:15:41,980 --> 00:15:43,440
Mr. Lin.

192
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:47,030
Look, I wanna say sorry about last night. You were right. I should have listened.

193
00:15:47,110 --> 00:15:49,950
